<p>How-To's:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sliderulemuseum.com/SR_Course.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sliderulemuseum.com/SR_Course.htm" rel="nofollow">International Slide Rule Museum</a> - Illustrated Self-Guided Course On How To Use The Slide Rule (with simulators)</li>
